column2: This was the best summer I have ever experienced.
I had a blast in california hanging out with my family and friends.
My best friend, her grandma doris and my sisterfriend planned a surprise baby shower for me and hailey on saturday.
Thank you so much for everyone who came.
:) Hailey recieved many gift cards (because I couldn't bring that much on the plane back home) and cute baby clothes and toys!!
So many lies about who you're talking to, where you're going, what you're doing.
My life is falling apart and I don't mean online.
I'm becoming a broken toy and now that I have had twelve (I counted) vials of blood drawn, I just feel like I'm compltely useless.
I broke my leg, and my head hurts, and Jack lost my money.
John and my friend planned a baby shower for me and cooked lunch.
